snippet.title: StarRunner - 2023 Basic 10Liner Contest Entry (Atari 8-bit)
snippet.description:
This is a video of my entry for the 2023 Basic 10Liner Contest ( https://basic10liner.com/ ) in the EXTREM-256 (256 characters per line) category.

It is running in the Atari Altirra Emulator (PAL mode).

It was written in FastBasic v4.6, using the cross compiler on PC/Mac.

Source code and more at the contest entry page:
https://bunsen.itch.io/starrunner-by-eric-carr
